lane_detection

Description:
	This directory contains a set of 
	important functions, that will allowed 
	the Intelligent Ground Vehicle do 
	detect lanes, and most of its content
	is inherate from kemfic's computer
	vision article "Curved Lane Detection"
	in hackster.io (https://www.hackster.io
	.../kemfic/curved-lane-detection-34f771

	The lane detection algorithm will follo
	w the following logic:
		distortion_Correction()
		perspective_Wrap()
		sobel_filter()
		histogramPeak_Detection()
		slidingWindow_Search()
		curve_fitting()
		detectedLane_Overlay()
		

